609
00:57:37,741 --> 00:57:40,208
Rym: If I don't have any powers, it's always the time boss.

610
00:57:41,110 --> 00:57:41,371
Scott: Sure.

611
00:57:42,654 --> 00:57:49,754
Scott: So yeah, so if you like an action RPG, if you like a roguelike, if you just like the story bits, right?

612
00:57:50,196 --> 00:57:57,060
